@NODE intro "Introduction"

This program gives a complete periodic system.
You can call various informations from the single elements.

Features of ChemicalDB:
* detailed informations to every element
* discoverer and their datas callable
* reactionformula incl. wordformula callable
* informations to subatomic particles
* chooseable periodic system layout (original periodic system/long periodic system)

@ENDNODE
