What is Freeware ?

Freeware you can copy and spread freely, as long as there is made no benefit
with the program, but the program-packet must be complete, which means there must be:

  - the program 	    "ChemicalDB"
  - the install-script	    "ChemicalDB.install"
  - this guide  	    "ChemicalDB.guide" (english and german)
  - the german catalog-file "Catalogs/deutsch/ChemicalDB.catalog"

If you are missing one of these files in the archive, please contact @{"me" link author} !

@ENDNODE
